name: Zeno
description: Zeno is the supreme being of the multiverse and has overwhelming power. The King of Everything, also known as Zen Oo (Zeno Sama in Spain and Zen Oo Sama in Latin America) and nicknamed by Son Goku as Todito (全ぜんちゃん, Zen-chan

originPlanet.name: Mobile Temple of the King of All
originPlanet.description: The mobile temple of the King of All (throne room), is as its name indicates, a mobile temple in which resides the thrones of the two Kings of All in the Survival Location in Dragon Ball Super.
